Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Fades towards the given color over the given time in seconds.

Usage
-----

*void* fadeIn( *vector* **color** , *float* **time** )

Parameters
----------

-   [color] - The color to fade to.
-   [time] - The duration of the fade.

Examples
--------

    Â 
    sys.fadeIn('0 0 0', 10);

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values.

